            "button_style": "btn--soft",
            "enable_video": false,
            "video_link": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc",
            "video_button_color": "text--white"
          }
        },
        "text_block_Wc8kNC": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "shape_class": "",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3><strong>Quality and Safety</strong></h3><h3></h3><p>At Time, we prioritize quality above all. Our sanitary pads undergo rigorous testing to ensure they meet the highest standards. You deserve nothing less than the best, and that's exactly what we deliver, Time Ultra-Thin Pads are made from materials that are gentle on your skin, ensuring Period Confidence, worry-free and comfortable experience.</p>",
